## Note for the user reviewing this

The article framed the demand-supply ratio as a one-line metric. In practice, "total short-form views in your niche" is fuzzy — what counts as "your niche," which platforms, which time window. We're keeping the wording loose ("rough math, not science") so the user uses it as a gate, not a precise instrument. If you want me to tighten it (e.g., "top 100 TikToks in the last 30 days under your top 3 keywords"), say the word and I'll revise.
